<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBrusco,_S.Castiglionesi,_F.2007" class="citation journal cs1">Brusco, S.; Castiglionesi, F. (2007). "Liquidity coinsurance, moral hazard, and financial contagion". <i>J Finance</i>. <b>62</b> (5): 2275–302. <a href="/wiki/CiteSeerX_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="CiteSeerX (identifier)">CiteSeerX</a>&#160;<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.410.8538">10.1.1.410.8538</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1540-6261.2007.01275.x">10.1111/j.1540-6261.2007.01275.x</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=J+Finance&amp;rft.atitle=Liquidity+coinsurance%2C+moral+hazard%2C+and+financial+contagion&amp;rft.volume=62&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=2275-302&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fciteseerx.ist.psu.edu%2Fviewdoc%2Fsummary%3Fdoi%3D10.1.1.410.8538%23id-name%3DCiteSeerX&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1111%2Fj.1540-6261.2007.01275.x&amp;rft.au=Brusco%2C+S.&amp;rft.au=Castiglionesi%2C+F.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABank+run" class="Z3988"></span></span>
